{"body": "Households are ineligible if, within three months before application or any time after certification, the household transfers a countable resource for less than its fair market value to qualify for assistance. This penalty applies if the total of the transferred resource added to other resources affects eligibility.\n\nResources transferred between members of the same TANF/SNAP household do not affect eligibility. If spouses separate and one spouse transfers individual property, the other spouse's eligibility is not affected.", "citation_label": "release scope us tx manual 2026 05 27 tx manuals 13", "citation_path": "us-tx/manual/recovery/release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals/block-13", "document_class": "manual", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "TANF and SNAP", "id": "4283284d-7e71-54bb-9b48-1028bc9bea41", "jurisdiction": "us-tx", "kind": "block", "language": "en", "level": 2, "metadata": {"block_count": 20, "content_type": null, "download_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/a-1210-general-policy", "fetched_at": "2026-07-13T23:11:39Z", "kind": "block", "recovery_parser": "documents:auto", "source_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/a-1210-general-policy", "title": "release scope us tx manual 2026 05 27 tx manuals"}, "ordinal": 13, "parent_citation_path": "us-tx/manual/recovery/release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals", "parent_id": "0162b845-f0d3-559d-b437-fb175e7240d0", "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_format": "html", "source_id": "release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals", "source_path": "sources/us-tx/manual/2026-07-13-recovery/official-documents/release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals", "source_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/a-1210-general-policy", "version": "2026-07-13-recovery"}
{"body": "Applicants or individuals who transfer resources to qualify for assistance must not be denied.", "citation_label": "release scope us tx manual 2026 05 27 tx manuals 14", "citation_path": "us-tx/manual/recovery/release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals/block-14", "document_class": "manual", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "Children on TP 56 and Children on TP 32", "id": "017d43ff-70c0-5ca2-9498-bf48a57a77b8", "jurisdiction": "us-tx", "kind": "block", "language": "en", "level": 2, "metadata": {"block_count": 20, "content_type": null, "download_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/a-1210-general-policy", "fetched_at": "2026-07-13T23:11:39Z", "kind": "block", "recovery_parser": "documents:auto", "source_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/a-1210-general-policy", "title": "release scope us tx manual 2026 05 27 tx manuals"}, "ordinal": 14, "parent_citation_path": "us-tx/manual/recovery/release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals", "parent_id": "0162b845-f0d3-559d-b437-fb175e7240d0", "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_format": "html", "source_id": "release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals", "source_path": "sources/us-tx/manual/2026-07-13-recovery/official-documents/release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals", "source_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/a-1210-general-policy", "version": "2026-07-13-recovery"}
