{"body": "The denial period begins in the application month unless the household is already certified when the advisor discovers the transfer.\n\nOnce the household is certified, the advisor must send a notice of adverse action and follow adverse action procedures. The advisor must begin the denial period the first month after the month the notice of adverse action expires unless the individual requests a fair hearing and receives continued benefits.", "citation_label": "release scope us tx manual 2026 05 27 tx manuals 20", "citation_path": "us-tx/manual/recovery/release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals/block-20", "document_class": "manual", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "TANF and SNAP", "id": "c34b2ae9-c031-5765-b40d-f8bac2aa1615", "jurisdiction": "us-tx", "kind": "block", "language": "en", "level": 2, "metadata": {"block_count": 20, "content_type": null, "download_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/a-1210-general-policy", "fetched_at": "2026-07-13T23:11:39Z", "kind": "block", "recovery_parser": "documents:auto", "source_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/a-1210-general-policy", "title": "release scope us tx manual 2026 05 27 tx manuals"}, "ordinal": 20, "parent_citation_path": "us-tx/manual/recovery/release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals", "parent_id": "0162b845-f0d3-559d-b437-fb175e7240d0", "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_format": "html", "source_id": "release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals", "source_path": "sources/us-tx/manual/2026-07-13-recovery/official-documents/release-scope-us-tx-manual-2026-05-27-tx-manuals", "source_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/a-1210-general-policy", "version": "2026-07-13-recovery"}
