{"body": "After eligibility is determined, the TANF grant amount is prorated for the first month of eligibility using the following steps:\n\nCalculate the certified group's recommended grant amount for the month based on the household size and net income. (See Step 5, line 3, page 3 of Form H1101 , TANF Worksheet , or Step 5, line 3, page 2 of Form H1102 , TANF Worksheet for Special Reviews and Denials .)\n\nDetermine the earlier of the certification date or the 30th day after the file date. Using the chart in C-112.1 , Proration Multiplier Chart , determine the appropriate proration multiplier.\n\nMultiply the recommended grant amount from Step 1 by the multiplier from Step 2.\n\nRound the amount from Step 3 down to the next dollar. If the resulting prorated grant is less than $10, the household is not eligible for a grant in the first month. The grant effective date is the first day of the following month.\n\nNote: One-Time TANF and One-Time TANF for Relatives payments are not prorated.", "citation_label": "us tx works handbook 5", "citation_path": "us-tx/manual/hhs/texas-works-handbook/c-110-tanf/block-5", "document_class": "manual", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "TANF", "id": "8323930b-cd7b-5c70-811d-9ebb14daaef9", "jurisdiction": "us-tx", "kind": "block", "language": "en", "level": 2, "metadata": {"block_count": 7, "content_type": null, "download_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/c-110-tanf", "fetched_at": "2026-07-14T01:42:28Z", "kind": "block", "recovery_parser": "new:texas-hhs-html", "source_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/c-110-tanf", "title": "us tx works handbook"}, "ordinal": 5, "parent_citation_path": "us-tx/manual/hhs/texas-works-handbook/c-110-tanf", "parent_id": "8dd840b3-2a9e-53b9-99cb-d2dad5dfde50", "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_format": "html", "source_id": "us-tx-works-handbook", "source_path": "sources/us-tx/manual/2026-07-13-recovery/official-documents/us-tx-works-handbook", "source_url": "https://www.hhs.texas.gov/handbooks/texas-works-handbook/c-110-tanf", "version": "2026-07-13-recovery"}
